! ASSERT_CONVENTION: natural_units=explicit_hbar_kB, fourier_convention=qe_bloch, xc_functional=PBEsol, pseudopotential=ONCV_PseudoDojo_PBEsol_stringent
!
! LaH10 (Fm-3m) DFPT phonon calculation at 170 GPa
! Computes dynamical matrices and electron-phonon matrix elements on coarse q-grid
!
! Coarse q-grid: 4x4x4 (LaH10 is ~15x more expensive than H3S per q-point
! due to 11-atom primitive cell vs 4-atom)
!
! KNOWN ISSUE: Harmonic DFPT for Fm-3m LaH10 may show soft modes
! near 170 GPa. Quantum nuclear effects (SSCHA) stabilize the structure
! (Errea et al., Nature 578, 66 (2020)). Marginally imaginary modes
! (< 20 cm^-1) at isolated q-points are acceptable.
!
! Expected computational cost: 24-72 hours on 16-32 cores
! Bottleneck: each irreducible q-point costs 3-10x an SCF calculation
!
Phonons of LaH10 at 170 GPa (Fm-3m)
&INPUTPH
  prefix       = 'lah10',
  outdir       = './tmp/',
  fildyn       = 'lah10.dyn',
  fildvscf     = 'dvscf',
  ldisp        = .true.,
  nq1          = 4,
  nq2          = 4,
  nq3          = 4,
  tr2_ph       = 1.0d-14,
  alpha_mix(1) = 0.3,
  nmix_ph      = 8,
  electron_phonon = 'interpolated',
  el_ph_sigma  = 0.005,
  el_ph_nsigma = 10,
/
